This directory contains some examples to help user understand the XORT package.

1. chado_dtd_creator.pl
   this will convert the DB schema into generic DTD. 

2. chado_xml_ann.xml
   game_xml_ann.xml
   chado_xml_ann_comp.xml
   game_xml_ann_comp.xml

Those are specific files for CHADO-Apollo project.
chado_xml_ann.xml   chado XML with ONE annotation
game_xml_ann.xml GAME xml corresponding to chado_xml_ann.xml

chado_xml_ann_comp.xml  chado XML with multiple annotationa and computational records
game_xml_ann_comp.xml  GAME xml corresponding to chado_xml_ann_comp.xml

The DTD for those two chado XML can be found in ../doc/chado.dtd

3. most of those files in this directory has been used for FlyBase project. Many can be re-used with minimal modification.